<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=1002751829153></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f1002751829153><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=journal.html?user=10704&mid=1002751829153>Day One - AM</a> <a id=fs8 href=journal.html?user=10704&mid=1002751829153#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=10704><span id=Scholar>The One and Only JanaLaser</span></a>, <span id=Scholar>Scholar</span><br><span id=notbold>22 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Wed, Oct 10th 6:10 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[4.50]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>It is the 5th Hour in Albion... I am awakened, but I feel fear and cannot open my eyes. I am not sure where or who or what I am. My mind is in turmoil. I cannot focus. Faces swirl by in the darkness, I feel pain in my heart, great pain and longing. I plead with the unknown. Please! help me...Time passes, a voice in my head, that is not mine, says that I am Nolarita, an Avalonian and that I must open my eyes and begin my life anew, but I am so alone, and there is one who calls to me from the darkness....and then he is gone, but the pain lingers around my heart like a cold fist clenching it...My own voice says not to be a coward, to get on with it and so I open my eyes. I see grey stone, massive walls. People run past me on all sides. I seem to know that I am in something called the Lethantis Association and that I must talk to the woman who is standing in front of me....I know that I have been before, but I know not where or how or when. I am aware that the clothing I am wearing is barely sufficient to keep out the damp let alone protect me from I know not what. I am feeling much anxiety, but also, a sense of wonder is coming upon me....I somehow recall being older, wiser, not this young, frightened woman who is still mostly girl. I decide to talk to the woman and take the first steps to recover from whatever has caused me to forget everything, somehow change from whomever I was and come to this place of mystery.........and so it begins anew.<br>&nbsp;<br>Nolarita Aurelius, <br>of DAoC, EQ, UO, and finest of all..Legends of Kesmai </td></tr>
